room_title: Escape room "The Illuminati Box" by UFO VIDEO in Gainesville
room_address: 605 NW 53rd Ave Suite A8a Gainesville, FL 32609
room_description: This is a challenging cryptography game loosely based on the world-famous Taman Shud mystery. This 90-minute game challenges players to learn and understand a series of complex codes in order to unlock a series of nested boxes and unpack their secrets. Winners take home a one-of-a-kind achievement trophy!
